"naked":


  tbl   Name               Role             
        Alice   Engineer   Berlin   Remote  


"all":

+-----+------------------+-----------------+
|     │ Name             │ Role            │
+ tbl +-------+----------+--------+--------+
|     │ Alice │ Engineer │ Berlin │ Remote │
+-----+-------+----------+--------+--------+


"header":

+-----+------------------+-----------------+
|     │ Name             │ Role            │
+ tbl +------------------+-----------------+
|     │ Alice   Engineer   Berlin   Remote │
+-----+-------+----------+--------+--------+


"no border":

 tbl  Name             Role           
      Alice  Engineer  Berlin  Remote 


WORKING EXAMPLE:

"all case"
+---+---+
│   │ B │
| A +---+
│   │ C │
+---+---+

"naked case"
         
      B  
  A      
      C  
         

"no borders case"
 A  B 
    C 
